social_posts.post_text: My sweet Ella Grace you are 5 today!!! Wow time sure flies when you are having fun. To be able to call you my daughter I’m blessed beyond measures. You’ll never understand truly how much you saved mommy & daddy. Ella Grace you are beautiful , you never meet a stranger, you are kind, you have a little sass, & you are MY BABYGIRL. I love you to infinity times a billion no matter what. I hope today is filled with mini brands and Oreo blizzards. You deserve the world & mommy and daddy will make sure you get nothing short of just that. 🥰😘🥹
Here’s to all the pain, crying, & happiness of 2022. Hope everyone knows 2023 WILL BE OUR YEAR 🥰. Thank you so much everyone for the continued support. Happy new years
Woah! 8 months sure make a difference. Still so crazy to think we have twins. You are the best dada🥹🥰😘

Im so glad I joined the hype about these flava purkles 🥰🥰. These pickles had me in a chokehold & they were so juicy. It’s the best packaging, great taste, & she just restocked back up. So that means y’all better grab them up 💕.

A huge shout out to @crazybellatransfers for helping us with our small business as well! We’ve got these amazing prints and uvdtf wraps. Y’all looking for sublimation or wrap? She’s your girl.!! The wrap, the sublimation prints, & the customer service is A+. She’s very helpful and will help you every step of the way! 🥰🥰🥰

Today was so bittersweet for me. My oldest baby graduated prek today 🥹. I was crying way before the program could get started. You’ve learned so much this year and created so many new friends (which I hear about each & everyday). We were blessed with great teachers for Ella’s first year of school and I’m beyond grateful for Ms.Hughes & Mr.Nesbitt. They always communicated with me and made this transition so easy for ella. Also to everyone who showed up for her this morning thank you for going above & beyond for Ella & always showing up for her. Now on to summer break and kindergarten. Congratulations my sweet ella Grace. We are so proud of you always 😍🥹.
WHO IS WATCHING TONIGHT? who will show up to mommas bridal shower? Ouhhhhh the surprise. This season is about to get juicy. Tune in tonight at 9pm est 🥰🥰.

The raw unedited version of alana graduating. To say im proud would be an understatement. To be there a witness this next chapter I’m amazed. Amazed at how much you’ve grown, how beautiful your soul is, & most importantly how far youve come against all odds. To hear your name be called & to watch you walk im honored truly. I cant wait to see what this next chapter in your life holds. Please always know im your biggest fan & always & forever gonna be screaming the loudest for you. I love you lana 🥰

A huge shoutout to @mshcreates again for making these beautiful signs for my sweetest babies 🥹😍. Every time she makes my ideas come to life & super quick 🫶🏼. Thank you for always coming through for all of the babies. Y’all better hit her up for all the birthday signs 😎😊.
When I say Marla understood the assignment & MORE SHE DID THAT & MORE!!! The customer service was 10/10. If y’all are needing a custom HAND PAINTED Stanley. Make sure to give her a follow 🥰🩷
Late night snack. Y’all already know @doreeshaflavadpuurckles . I’m not usually a pickle person but these mf SLAP. y’all place your orders and tell her mama p sent you 😘
